00:39:59,363 --> 00:40:01,164
How long have you worked here?

502
00:40:01,166 --> 00:40:03,133
Um, two months.

503
00:40:05,803 --> 00:40:09,038
So... what's her story?

504
00:40:12,476 --> 00:40:14,811
Oh, what's to tell?

505
00:40:14,813 --> 00:40:17,947
Um, she was in a band
