506
00:40:17,949 --> 00:40:19,949
Wannabe rock star and all that.

507
00:40:19,951 --> 00:40:22,752
Uh, she drank a lot,

508
00:40:22,754 --> 00:40:25,455
took pills, got pregnant.

509
00:40:25,457 --> 00:40:29,225
Her life fell apart,
and her daughter OD'd at 19.

510
00:40:29,227 --> 00:40:32,996
And I think that's probably
one of her T-shirts.

511
00:40:44,141 --> 00:40:46,142
What's up?

512
00:40:46,144 --> 00:40:47,811
Nothing.

513
00:40:49,447 --> 00:40:51,080
Okay.

514
00:41:06,464 --> 00:41:07,964
How did you like your massage?

515
00:41:07,966 --> 00:41:10,700
- It's nice. It's...
- They're so great here.

516
00:41:10,702 --> 00:41:12,936
- The best ever, right?
- Amen.

517
00:41:12,938 --> 00:41:15,572
Oh, I wouldn't know.
That was my first one.

518
00:41:15,574 --> 00:41:17,974
Where are you from, Gracie?

519
00:41:17,976 --> 00:41:20,176
New York.
Wow!

520
00:41:20,178 --> 00:41:21,911
Have you ever been
to a Broadway show?

521
00:41:21,913 --> 00:41:24,013
I'm not actually from the city.

522
00:41:24,015 --> 00:41:26,416
My dad works there,
but I don't go there very much.

523
00:41:26,418 --> 00:41:28,751
- I'd love to see a Broadway show.
- What does he do?

524
00:41:28,753 --> 00:41:31,120
I don't know.
He wears a suit.

525
00:41:31,122 --> 00:41:34,524
Aw, that's okay, honey. More
